Introduction

Son Yewon is a South Korean singer and composer under ATTRAKT. She is best known as the lead vocalist and lead dancer of the girl group FIFTY FIFTY.

In June 2023, she participated in the reality survival show R U Next?. She was eliminated in the episode 6 after achieving 18th place.

On August 12, 2024, Yewon was the fourth member of FIFTY FIFTY to be revealed. She debuted on August 30, 2024, with the group's pre-release single "Starry Night".
